snippet.title: Sacra Terra: Kiss of Death PSN [Official Trailer]
snippet.description:
Download Sacra Terra: Kiss of Death on PSN! https://store.sonyentertainmentnetwork.com/#!/en-us/games/sacra-terra-kiss-of-death/cid=UP4173-NPUB31520_00-SACRATERRA000000

Guide a woman who sets out rescue her fiancé from a supernatural force that feeds on human suffering! As she explores visually stunning mystical dimensions in a bid to reunite other lovers and weaken the grip of the entity, you'll find useful items, solve puzzles and enjoy a richly layered and compelling hidden object experience!
